    public class CloseTicketFragment
extends TicketFragment
    It's a concrete implementation of TicketFragment to display closed tickets only. In this version of TicketFragment, only informatory part will be displayed on the screen. In the beginning, FloatingActionButton to update and re locate user on the map will be hidden. Because no current location will be displayed on this fragment and user can not update any task status here.
